ServiceNow Table API CRUD Operations Using Postman

Learn how to perform Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD) operations on a custom ServiceNow table using the Table API and Postman.

📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how external applications interact with ServiceNow through REST APIs. Using Postman, I performed complete CRUD operations on a custom table (u_test1) by sending HTTP requests and handling JSON responses.

✨ Features
Retrieve all records
Retrieve a specific record
Create a new record
Update an existing record
Delete a record
Basic Authentication
JSON Request & Response
HTTP Status Codes
